        <h1>Arctic Sea Ice</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Visualizing sea ice loss over decades</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="location-info">
            <p>The Arctic is warming twice as fast as the global average, leading to dramatic sea ice decline. Summer ice extent and thickness have decreased, impacting Arctic ecosystems and global climate.</p>
            <p>Loss of ice affects wildlife like polar bears and accelerates global warming due to reduced albedo, making the region critical for climate monitoring.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="comparison-container">
            <div class="comparison-item">
