        <section class="impact-section">
            <h2>Environmental Impacts</h2>
            <div class="impact-grid">
                <div class="impact-card">
                    <h3>Sea Level Rise</h3>
                    <p>As glaciers and ice sheets melt, they contribute directly to global sea level rise, threatening coastal communities worldwide.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-card">
                    <h3>Biodiversity Loss</h3>
                    <p>Habitat destruction and changing conditions threaten countless species with extinction, disrupting ecosystems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-card">
                    <h3>Albedo Effect</h3>
                    <p>As reflective ice is replaced by darker water or land, less sunlight is reflected back to space, accelerating warming.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="impact-card">
                    <h3>Extreme Weather</h3>
                    <p>Climate change intensifies hurricanes, droughts, heatwaves, and floods, causing widespread damage and displacement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="call-to-action">
            <h2>Be Part of the Solution</h2>
            <p>While the changes we see in these images can be alarming, there is still time to take action. Every effort to reduce our carbon footprint matters.</p>
            <a href="https://climate.nasa.gov/solutions/" class="btn" target="_blank">Learn How You Can Help</a>
        </section>
